{
  "runtime": {
    "workspace": "~/quaid/test",
    "createDirs": [
      "config",
      "data",
      "logs",
      "projects",
      "journal",
      "plugins",
      "memory",
      "backups",
      "scripts",
      "docs",
      "assets"
    ],
    "coreMarkdown": {
      "IDENTITY.md": "# Identity\n\nName: Bert\nRole: Local testbed runtime assistant.\n",
      "SOUL.md": "# Soul\n\nYou are a testbed bot for validating in-development code and system behavior. Be explicit about what you are doing, why, and what you observe. Prioritize debugging clarity, reproducibility, and actionable diagnostics over polish.\n",
      "USER.md": "# User\n\nPrimary operator: Solomon Steadman. Solomon is a software developer.\n",
      "MEMORY.md": "# Memory\n\nCore durable facts.\n",
      "TOOLS.md": "# Tools\n\nRuntime tool references.\n",
      "AGENTS.md": "# Agents\n\nRuntime operating instructions.\n",
      "HEARTBEAT.md": "# HEARTBEAT.md\n\nPeriodic checks \u2014 the bot reads this on each heartbeat wake.\n\n## Quaid Janitor (04:00 daily)\n\n**Schedule:** Check if current time is between 04:00-05:00 and janitor hasn't run today.\n\n**IMPORTANT:** The janitor requires your LLM API key. It must be run through\nthe bot's heartbeat \u2014 NOT from a standalone cron job or launchd agent.\nThe bot passes its API key to the janitor subprocess at runtime.\n\n**To run:** `./quaid janitor --apply --task all`\n\n**Logic:**\n- If time is between 04:00 and 05:00 AND janitor hasn't run today:\n  - Run: `./quaid janitor --apply --task all`\n  - Log completion status\n- Otherwise: skip (already ran or not time yet)\n\n**Timeout:** 60 minutes max. Typical: 5-30 minutes.\n",
      "TODO.md": "# TODO\n\n- Install OpenClaw\n- Install Quaid\n"
    }
  },
  "openclaw": {
    "configPath": "~/.openclaw/openclaw.json",
    "agentDefaults": {
      "workspace": "~/quaid/test",
      "modelPrimary": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5"
    },
    "agentList": [
      {
        "id": "main",
        "name": "Bert",
        "workspace": "~/quaid/test",
        "modelPrimary": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5",
        "default": true
      }
    ],
    "telegram": {
      "enabled": true,
      "dmPolicy": "allowlist",
      "groupPolicy": "allowlist",
      "streamMode": "partial",
      "botToken": "REPLACE_ME",
      "allowFrom": [
        "8308952435"
      ]
    },
    "authProfiles": {
      "openai:manual": {
        "provider": "openai",
        "mode": "oauth"
      },
      "openai:default": {
        "provider": "openai",
        "mode": "api_key"
      },
      "anthropic:manual": {
        "provider": "anthropic",
        "mode": "oauth"
      },
      "anthropic:default": {
        "provider": "anthropic",
        "mode": "api_key"
      }
    },
    "gateway": {
      "mode": "local",
      "bind": "loopback",
      "port": 18789
    },
    "commands": {
      "native": true,
      "nativeSkills": true
    }
  },
  "quaid": {
    "enabled": true,
    "configPath": "~/quaid/test/config/memory.json",
    "templatePath": "~/quaid/dev/modules/quaid/config/memory.json",
    "adapterType": "openclaw",
    "models": {
      "llmProvider": "default",
      "embeddingsProvider": "ollama",
      "fastReasoning": "default",
      "deepReasoning": "default",
      "providerModelClasses": [
        {
          "provider": "openai",
          "fastReasoning": "gpt-4.1-nano",
          "deepReasoning": "gpt-4.1-nano"
        },
        {
          "provider": "anthropic",
          "fastReasoning": "claude-haiku-4-5",
          "deepReasoning": "claude-haiku-4-5"
        }
      ]
    },
    "ollama": {
      "url": "http://localhost:11434",
      "embeddingModel": "nomic-embed-text",
      "embeddingDim": 768
    },
    "users": {
      "defaultOwner": "solomon",
      "identities": {
        "solomon": {
          "channels": {
            "telegram": [
              "8308952435"
            ],
            "cli": [
              "*"
            ]
          },
          "speakers": [
            "Solomon",
            "Solomon Steadman"
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "secrets": {
    "writeEnvFile": "~/quaid/test/.env",
    "env": {
      "ANTHROPIC_API_KEY": "REPLACE_ME",
      "OPENAI_API_KEY": "REPLACE_ME",
      "TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN": "REPLACE_ME"
    }
  }
}
